                    <h1>"Nectar Language Reference"</h1>
                <p>"This document is the reference for the Nectar programming language. It covers every language construct, from lexical structure to templates, with syntax, semantics, and examples."</p>
                <blockquote>
                    <p><strong>"Accuracy note"</strong>": Features marked with "<strong>"(PLANNED)"</strong>" are parsed by the compiler but do not yet have working codegen or runtime support. Do not rely on them for production code. Everything else compiles to working WASM."</p>
